OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA damp end
OL,6,Fto the day with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fcontinuing to clear eastwards. Turning
OL,8,Fdrier overnight with a mixture of
OL,9,Fclear spells and isolated showers.
OL,10,FMilder than last night and staying
OL,11,Ffrost-free.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,14,Fisolated showers until late afternoon,
OL,15,Fthen the showers become more
OL,16,Fwidespread and sometimes heavy, with a
OL,17,Fsmall chance of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
